<subSubSection id="1C8865384C578B15D5F1F7070660FCE0" pageId="11" pageNumber="72" type="reference_group">
<paragraph id="542D36B34C578B15D5F1F7070660FCE0" blockId="11.[136,1452,626,833]" pageId="11" pageNumber="72">
<taxonomicName id="93924D304C578B15D5F1F70702EFFD2D" authority="Ramirez &amp; Sala" authorityName="Ramirez &amp; Sala" box="[136,504,626,652]" class="Bacillariophyceae" family="Surirellaceae" genus="Surirella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Chromista" order="Surirellales" pageId="11" pageNumber="72" phylum="Bacillariophyta" rank="species" species="rafaelii">
<emphasis id="66E6EAA14C578B15D5F1F7070255FD2D" box="[136,322,626,652]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="72">Surirella rafaelii</emphasis>
Ramírez &amp; Sala
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="93924D304C578B15D752F706060FFD2C" authority="Medina Tombe, Sala, Vouilloud &amp; Ramirez Restrepo" authorityName="Medina Tombe, Sala, Vouilloud &amp; Ramirez Restrepo" authorityYear="2016" box="[555,1304,626,653]" class="Bacillariophyceae" family="Surirellaceae" genus="Surirella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Chromista" order="Surirellales" pageId="11" pageNumber="72" phylum="Bacillariophyta" rank="species" species="tayronarum">
<emphasis id="66E6EAA14C578B15D752F70601DEFD2D" box="[555,713,627,653]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="72">S. tayronarum</emphasis>
Medina Tombé, Sala, Vouilloud &amp; Ramírez Restrepo
</taxonomicName>
, two recently described species from 
<collectingCountry id="2C8576234C578B15D4EBF7E30117FD11" box="[402,512,662,688]" name="Colombia" pageId="11" pageNumber="72">Colombia</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="30034B424C578B15D769F7E301D5FD11" author="Sala, S. E. &amp; Ramirez, J. J. &amp; Vouilloud, A. A. &amp; Plata-Diaz C." box="[528,706,662,689]" pageId="11" pageNumber="72" pagination="17 - 35" refId="ref10507" refString="Sala, S. E., Ramirez, J. J., Vouilloud, A. A. &amp; Plata-Diaz C., Y. (2013) Surirella antioquiensis sp. nov. and S. rafaelii sp. nov. (Bacillariophyta) from Colombia Acta Nova 6: 17 - 35." type="journal article" year="2013">
Sala 
<emphasis id="66E6EAA14C578B15D730F7E2016CFD11" box="[585,635,662,688]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="72">et al</emphasis>
. 2013
</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="30034B424C578B15D780F7E30730FD11" author="Medina Tombe, M. F. &amp; Sala, S. E. &amp; Vouilloud, A. A. &amp; Ramirez Restrepo, J. J." box="[761,1063,662,689]" pageId="11" pageNumber="72" pagination="39 - 47" refId="ref9796" refString="Medina Tombe, M. F., Sala, S. E., Vouilloud, A. A. &amp; Ramirez Restrepo, J. J. (2016) Surirella tayronarum spec. nov. (Surirellaceae, Bacillariophyta) from Colombia. Phytotaxa 278: 39 - 47. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / phytotaxa. 278.1.4" type="journal article" year="2016">
Medina Tombé 
<emphasis id="66E6EAA14C578B15D6D2F7E200CAFD11" box="[939,989,662,688]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="72">et al</emphasis>
. 2016
</bibRefCitation>
, respectively), formerly belonging to the Robustae group of the genus 
<taxonomicName id="93924D304C578B15D762F7CF0169FD75" authorityName="Turpin" authorityYear="1828" box="[539,638,698,724]" class="Bacillariophyceae" family="Surirellaceae" genus="Surirella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Chromista" order="Surirellales" pageId="11" pageNumber="72" phylum="Bacillariophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="66E6EAA14C578B15D762F7CF0169FD75" box="[539,638,698,724]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="72">Surirella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, which has been accommodated within 
<taxonomicName id="93924D304C578B15D13AF7CF0788FD75" authority="A.Jurilj, 1949" authorityName="Jurilj" authorityYear="1949" box="[1091,1183,698,724]" class="Bacillariophyceae" family="Surirellaceae" genus="Iconella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Chromista" order="Surirellales" pageId="11" pageNumber="72" phylum="Ochrophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="66E6EAA14C578B15D13AF7CF0788FD75" box="[1091,1183,698,724]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="72">Iconella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="30034B424C578B15D1B3F7CF06BFFD74" author="Ruck, E. C. &amp; Nakov, T. &amp; Alverson, A. J. &amp; Theriot, E. C." box="[1226,1448,698,725]" pageId="11" pageNumber="72" pagination="155 - 171" refId="ref10153" refString="Ruck, E. C., Nakov, T., Alverson, A. J. &amp; Theriot, E. C. (2016 a) Phylogeny, ecology, morphological evolution, and reclassification of the diatom orders Surirellales and Rhopalodiales. Molecular Phylogenetics and Evolution 103: 155 - 171. https: // doi. org / 10.1016 / j. ympev. 2016.07.023" type="journal article" year="2016">
Ruck 
<emphasis id="66E6EAA14C578B15D074F7CE0628FD75" box="[1293,1343,698,724]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="72">et al</emphasis>
. (2016a)
</bibRefCitation>
. Both species have a raphe canal raised above valve face and mantle and alar canals with fenestral openings occluded by fenestral bars and internally with rimmed pores, thus exhibiting the diagnostic characters of the re-established genus (
<bibRefCitation id="30034B424C578B15D5E9F653024DFCE1" author="Ruck, E. C. &amp; Nakov, T. &amp; Alverson, A. J. &amp; Theriot, E. C." box="[144,346,806,833]" pageId="11" pageNumber="72" pagination="155 - 171" refId="ref10153" refString="Ruck, E. C., Nakov, T., Alverson, A. J. &amp; Theriot, E. C. (2016 a) Phylogeny, ecology, morphological evolution, and reclassification of the diatom orders Surirellales and Rhopalodiales. Molecular Phylogenetics and Evolution 103: 155 - 171. https: // doi. org / 10.1016 / j. ympev. 2016.07.023" type="journal article" year="2016">
Ruck 
<emphasis id="66E6EAA14C578B15D5AAF6520212FCE1" box="[211,261,806,832]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="72">et al</emphasis>
. 2016a
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="30034B424C578B15D41FF653010BFCE1" author="Jahn, R. &amp; Kusber, W. - H. &amp; Cocquyt, C." box="[358,540,806,833]" pageId="11" pageNumber="72" pagination="73 - 112" refId="ref9203" refString="Jahn, R., Kusber, W. - H. &amp; Cocquyt, C. (2017) Differentiating Iconella from Surirella (Bacillariophyceae): Typifying four Ehrenberg names and a preliminary checklist of the African taxa. PhytoKeys 82: 73 - 112. https: // doi. org / 10.3897 / phytokeys. 82.13542" type="journal article" year="2017">
Jahn 
<emphasis id="66E6EAA14C578B15D4D9F65202C6FCE1" box="[416,465,806,832]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="72">et al</emphasis>
. 2017
</bibRefCitation>
). Therefore, we here propose the formal transfer of these species to 
<taxonomicName id="93924D304C578B15D06AF6530678FCE1" authority="A.Jurilj, 1949" authorityName="Jurilj" authorityYear="1949" box="[1299,1391,806,832]" class="Bacillariophyceae" family="Surirellaceae" genus="Iconella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Chromista" order="Surirellales" pageId="11" pageNumber="72" phylum="Ochrophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="66E6EAA14C578B15D06AF6530678FCE1" box="[1299,1391,806,832]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="72">Iconella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
:
</paragraph>
